        public java.util.concurrent.Future<java.lang.String> subscribeAndListen​(int port,
                                                                        java.lang.String ip)
                                                                 throws java.lang.Exception
        this operation subscribe yourself on Orion to receive notifications about changed values
        Parameters:
        port - an given port from where the br.com.ufs.orionframework.server is listening.
        ip - an given IP address from where the br.com.ufs.orionframework.server is running.
        Returns:
        a Future value, to retrieve the br.com.ufs.orionframework.entity value, you must use this method and call getSubscriptionUpdate method after.

        java.lang.Exception
